# AI Planning MCP Server - Complete Workflow Guide

**Version:** 0.5.0
**Last Updated:** 2025-10-26

## Overview

This guide provides a complete start-to-finish workflow demonstrating how the AI Planning MCP Server facilitates comprehensive goal lifecycle management. The server provides 11 tools across 5 phases that work together to transform ideas into completed projects.

---

